{"tid":664659,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"電車早25秒發車被投訴　日本鐵道公司道歉","createTime":"2018-05-14T09:17:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T09:04:36.000Z","uid":184679,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4d7102930ae30e5cb5203ee25cfb35d2d75e8b3f","tid":664659,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T09:17:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180513/1353086/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180513%2F1353086%2F&d=jP1xHi%2F8I8lBzWYhOTrsJzACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=a500f24b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180513%2F1353086%2F&h=76dc3c38\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180513/1353086/</a><br />\n<br />\n日本電車因為早25秒發車，導致部分乘客沒搭到車憤而投訴，鐵道公司出面道歉表示會避免同樣的狀況再度發生。<br />\n<br />\n據《朝日新聞》報導，JR西日本，11日早上7點12分於能登川站發車的琵琶湖線新快速電車，因為早25秒發車，導致有數名乘客沒搭到車。JR西日本說明，電車車掌於11分時將車門關閉後，確認月台上沒有其他乘客後才發車。不過實際上月台上還有數名乘客，一名男乘客投訴「比預定時間還早發車」，讓JR西日本出面道歉「造成乘客困擾感到相當抱歉，將徹底執行基本確認動作，努力避免事件再度發生」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be9ed4aea5acd9ae84d9a44c7528d1ea95f4549c","tid":664659,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T09:18:59.000Z","msg":"JR.."},{"pid":"0b9922d6b5ad4f8037b2ff5d95c10fa76cdeb1fd","tid":664659,"uid":52605,"like":5,"dislike":12,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T09:20:36.000Z","msg":"我覺得好痴線 得幾條友搭唔到車就要道歉<br />\n基本上好多地方都同你講:早到係你既責任"},{"pid":"294b7b5e4a4004d8a25ac25591419f178f0d1dd2","tid":664659,"uid":60366,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T09:21:33.000Z","msg":"啱啱我個老死困左係 Sydney train上面兩粒鐘<br />\n無冷氣無燈無得開窗<br />\n<br />\n仲要無得退錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8004779b8cad62a07c01809c54c301db1bce0dd","tid":664659,"uid":35